casebody.head_matter:
John E. WINFIELD, applicant,
v.
George A. LOMBARDI, Director, Missouri Department of Corrections, et al.
No. 13A1231.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 17, 2014.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied.
Justice SOTOMAYOR would grant the application for stay of execution.
